<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_78" id="38r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_78_r1l6">Rıtter <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Ortolff göſſen ʒu ydem </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_78_r1l7"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Ortolff / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / es ſey an eẅch <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wıe eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l8">ſun Görg Göſſ in einr abſag ſüll <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſteen dıe vns <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l9">von flednicʒ ſelıg geſant ſüll <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd Jm doch nıht <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l10">vmb ſölıch <expan>entſag<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd er meyne vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu dıenen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l11">Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ vns auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l12">niht <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ıſt daʒ der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> eẅr ſune görg göſſ in keinr abſag gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l13">vns begrıffen ſey vnd wır <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt Jm <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> niht ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l14"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vnd guts / <expan>deſgleıche<ex>n</ex></expan> wır vns ʒu Jm auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l15"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſehen</expan> / Vnd getrawen eẅch auch wol Jr wellet den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> eẅr <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_r1l16">vnd <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> tun wo das an eẅch gelange . / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_78_line_1577025839562_4169">lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> thome <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_78" id="38r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ritter <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Ortolff Gössen zu Ydem</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Ortolff, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, es sey an ewch
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie ewr sun Görg Göss in einr absag
                        süll <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> steen, die uns
                            <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Flednicz selig gesant süll
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und im doch niht
                                <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> sey umb sölich
                                <expan>entsag<ex>en</ex></expan> und er meyne, uns und den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu dienen, etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> daz, uns auch niht
                            <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ist, daz der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>, ewr sune Görg Göss, in keinr
                        absag gen uns begriffen sey und wir <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> zu disen
                                <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> mit im <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                        niht zu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, denn <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und
                        guts, <expan>desgleiche<ex>n</ex></expan> wir uns zu im auch
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sehen</expan>. Und getrawen ewch auch wol, ir
                        wellet den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ewr
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und
                            <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> tun, wo das an ewch gelange. Denn
                        wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Thome <expan>App<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
